    <title>Template: Accessibility Requirements</title>
    <contents>

      <table class="table table-striped" aria-labelledby="h1_title">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th scope="col" style="min-width: 16em">Success Criterion</th>
            <th scope="col">Level</th>
            <th scope="col">Requirement</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td scope="row">
              <a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG/#info-and-relationships" target="_spec">1.3.1 Info and Relationships</a>
            </td>
            <td>A</td>
            <td>Use of <code>nav</code> element to create a navigation landmark region to identify the menu of links.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td scope="row">
              <a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG/#meaningful-sequence" target="_spec">1.3.2 Meaningful Sequence</a>
            </td>
            <td>A</td>
            <td>The template implements meaningful sequence by identifying the header, main and footer information in a logical order.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td scope="row">
              <a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG/#reflow" target="_spec">1.4.10 Reflow</a>
            </td>
            <td>AA</td>
            <td>Using a responsive design and media queries our template works on very narrow renderings.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td scope="row">
              <a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG/#bypass-blocks" target="_spec">2.4.1 Bypass Blocks</a>
            </td>
            <td>A</td>
            <td>Using <a href="https://github.com/a11y-tools/skipto/blob/master/README.md">SkipTo script</a> to implement bypass requirement.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td scope="row">
              <a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG/#bypass-blocks" target="_spec">2.4.2 Page Titled</a>
            </td>
            <td>A</td>
            <td>The <code>php</code> script automatically updates the <code>title</code> element with the <code>h1</code> element content.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td scope="row">
              <a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG/#multiple-ways" target="_spec">2.4.5 Multiple Ways</a>
            </td>
            <td>AA</td>
            <td>The banner navigation menu and the search function provide two ways to find and navigate to pages in the website.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td scope="row">
              <a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG/#headings-and-labels" target="_spec">2.4.6 Headings and Labels</a>
            </td>
            <td>AA</td>
            <td>The landmarks are properly labelled and headings are used in a structural way.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td scope="row">
              <a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG/#headings-and-labels" target="_spec">3.1.1 Language of Page</a>
            </td>
            <td>A</td>
            <td>Include the <code>lang</code> attribute on the <code>html</code> element.</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
